        "SANDSWEPT_SHRINE_DEATH_DESCRIPTION": "激活时，死亡神龛消耗幸存者{percentHealthCost}%的生命值并禁用所有治疗{healingDisableDuration}秒，但有{onKillProcChance}%概率触发击杀效果，{onInteractProcChance}%概率触发互动效果。",

        "SANDSWEPT_VOLTAIC_DRONE_BODY": "伏打无人机",
        "SANDSWEPT_VOLTAIC_DRONE_BROKEN_NAME": "损坏的伏打无人机",
